variables.name: Image Prompt
variables.description: describe this image with tons of details as if you were a Reverse Prompt Engineer to be able to create the exact same image using the prompt.

variables.name: Video Prompt
variables.description: i want to create a stunning video from this image , provide a detailed prompt to generate a stunning video from this image. Include Camera movement, composition and every detail you can. Respond in prompt format
